<header>
  <p>Never forget anything again.</p>
  <h1>7kai Tasks</h1>
  <nav><a
    data-setup="show"
    data-show='{"id":"signin"}'
  ><img src="/static/img/button-start.gif"></a></nav>
  <div class="container">
    <div
      class="row"
      style="cursor: pointer"
      data-setup="show"
      data-show='{"id":"screenshot"}'
    >
      <div class="span4 offset2">
        <div class="thumbnail"><img src="/static/img/tasks-home.png"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="span4">
        <div class="thumbnail"><img src="/static/img/tasks-gantt.png"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
<article>
  <ul class="unstyled">
    <li>
			<div>
      	<span>The web-based task management software.</span>
      	<a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
    	</div>
		</li>
    <li>
      <div>
				<span>Collaborations with your friend of Twitter and Facebook.</span>
	      <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
			</div>
			<div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Assign members to a list.</h2>
          <p></p>
        </div>
	      <div class="span6 thumbnail">
	        <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-social.png">
	      </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Easily a rescheduling by the Gantt chart.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-gantt.png">
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Use the cursor control keys or click cell.</h2>
          <p>
            Selection task ... [Top] / [Down].<br>
            Setting due dates ... [Left] / [Right].
          </p>
          <p>
            It is caused by a bad tool that a date is vague.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Display only an available list depending on the situation.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Classify lists with a color.</h2>
          <p>Work and a private or importance ...etc</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-tag2.png">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Can be used as a filter.</h2>
          <p></p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-tag.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Obvious from the counter.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-filter.png">
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Quick Filter with a counter.</h2>
          <p>
            When Verify was 1, somebody fixed your request.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>It is not counted when I make pending.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Pending Task.</h2>
          <p>If a list and the task that are not active are pending, you can concentrate on your playing.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-flexible.png">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Pending List.</h2>
          <p>It is an idea to make a list to collect pending task.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-pending-list.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Subscribe in RSS Reader.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-format.png">
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Supports many public formats.</h2>
          <p>RSS, iCal, HTML, JSON, JSONP.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Check in Browser Extensions.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Chrome Extensions.</h2>
          <p>Even if you do not open the page, extensions displayed number of todo.</p>
          <p><strong>Never forget anything again.</strong></p>
          <p><a href="https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/dolhpjcchfcnkcanamhgcgbnmcogdank" target="_blank">7kai Tasks Checker (Chrome Web Store)</a></p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-ext.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Once you learn a few shortcut keys and get comfortable.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-key.png">
        </div>
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Display the Shortcut Keys.</h2>
          <p>click keyboard icon or press [?] or [/] key.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div>
        <span>Easily a move and hierarchy setting by the Drag and Drop.</span>
        <a><img src="/static/img/button-cross.gif"></a>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Move to under the task.</h2>
          <p>Drop to a Task.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-nest.png">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Move to the root.</h2>
          <p>Drop to a Space.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-nest2.png">
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="span6">
          <h2>Move to the list.</h2>
          <p>Drop to a list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="span6 thumbnail">
          <img src="/static/img/tasks-concept-dd-list.png">
        </div>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>
</article>
